data.description: Honey, stop the car! This adorable and spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home is within walking distance to Lake Ariana. This home features luxury vinyl plank flooring (2020), fresh interior paint (2020), a newer roof (2017) and a new A/C handler (2021). The kitchen has been updated with granite counter tops, beautiful white cabinets and a nook perfect for breakfast with the family. Cozy up in the living room around the wood-burning fireplace and watch all your favorite movies on the 120-inch projector screen. Both bathrooms are updated with tile showers, tile flooring and stone counter vanities. You'll love the privacy this home provides with a split floor plan and oversized bedrooms. Have a seat on the large back or front porch and listen to the breeze flow through the mature oak trees that were trimmed this year. This home is located just 5 miles from I-4 and 2 miles away from downtown Auburndale. This home has been priced UNDER market value for a quick sale. With all the features and a great price, this home won't last long! The sellers are now offering a $1,000 credit to add flooring to the 4th bedroom.
